skin-803657465fa6_0_st.name: StatTrak™ USP-S | Jawbreaker (Factory New)
skin-803657465fa6_0_st.description:
This item features StatTrak™ technology, which tracks certain statistics when equipped by its owner.

This item tracks Confirmed Kills.

A fan favorite from Counter-Strike Source, the Silenced USP Pistol has a detachable silencer that gives shots less recoil while suppressing attention-getting noise. This custom painted USP-S uses high gloss paint and depicts a dog barking from the grip to the silencer. The silencer reads \"GOOD DOGGY\".\n\nI said \"sit\"!
